high_descs: Turn around and head straight, then turn left at the fridge to continue to stand at the counter left of the sink.
Pick up the butter knife from the sink.
Move to stand in front of the sink, which is to your right.
Slice the apple on the counter by the salt shaker to the right of the sink.
Turn and carry the knife to the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge on the shelf next to the tomato.
Turn around and head back to the sliced apple on the counter by the sink.
Pick up a slice of apple from the counter.
Turn around and carry the slice of apple to the fridge.
Place the apple slice in the fridge on the shelf left of the tomato, close the door, and then remove after a few seconds.
Turn around and after a couple steps, turn left to move to stand in front of the stove while carrying the apple slice.
Place the apple slice in the microwave above the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold slice of apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter on the left of the sink.
Pick up the gray knife on the counter.
Turn right and go to the front of the sink.
Cut the red apple on the right of the sink next to the salt shaker.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator across the kitchen.
Place the knife in the refrigerator on the right of the red tomato.
Turn around and go back to the counter on the right of the sink.
Pick up one piece of the cut apple on the counter.
Turn around and go to the front of the refrigerator.
Chill the cut apple on the left side on the red tomato and take it out.
Turn right to go to the microwave above the stove.
Place the apple piece on the left of the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled piece of apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Go to the counter left of the sink
Pick up a butterknife from the counter
Go to the sink
Cut the apple next to the sink
Go to the fridge
Place the butterknife in the fridge
Go to the sink
Pick up the apple piece next to the sink
Go to the fridge
Chill the apple piece in the fridge

Place the apple piece in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled apple piece in a microwave
